\begin{chaptersum}
\begin{itemize}[nosep]
\item 18 agent types on a 3D discrete grid with continuous glucose overlay
\item 14-field effect system mediates paracrine signaling between agents
\item Deferred movement pattern eliminates activation-order bias
\item Four terminal conditions ensure definitive simulation outcomes
\end{itemize}
\end{chaptersum}

